    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-07-27T19:53:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1950-07-27T19:53:00-05:00" n="144"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d144">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">330/7–2750: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The United States Representative at the United Nations</hi>
                        (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Austin</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New York</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1950-07-27T20:53:00-04:00"
                            >July 27, 1950—8:53 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>146. Following is text of Malik (USSR) communication to <gloss target="#t_UN1"
                        >UN</gloss>
                    <gloss target="#t_SYG1">SYG</gloss> re August <gloss target="#t_SC1">SC</gloss>:
                    (Doc./1643):</p>
                <quote rend="blockquote">
                    <p>“I consider it necessary to inform you that, in accordance with established
                        procedure, I am assuming the presidency of the <gloss target="#t_SC1"
                            >SC</gloss> in August of this year and that I am setting the date of the
                        meeting of the Council for 1 August at 3 p. m.</p>
                    <p>“I request you to arrange to notify the members of the <gloss target="#t_SC1"
                            >SC</gloss> regarding the date of the meeting.</p>
                    <p>“The agenda will be communicated subsequently.”</p>
                </quote>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Austin</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
